data.description: Step into Your Dream Home! This stunning single-family residence doesn't just boast 2 spacious bedrooms and 2 elegant bathrooms – it comes with a bonus big-sized sunny room as a 3rd bedroom and a dedicated dining area. As you step into the modern kitchen, you'll be inspired by its sleek stainless steel appliances.  The brand-new roof and solar panel system ensure both energy efficiency. With hurricane-proof windows and doors, you can enjoy your peace.  No HOA fees! This recently renovated gem also features a brand-new fence, guaranteeing both privacy and security. Located at a prime corner, this house is an excellent investment opportunity for Airbnb. Meticulously maintained and freshly painted. The seller gives $10,000 credit at closing!
